casebody.data:
WINN & LOVETT GROCERY COMPANY v. MEARL F. FARRINGTON. 24 So. (2nd) 111

June Term, 1945

December 18, 1945 Division B Howell, McCarthy, Lane & Howell, Charles Cook Howell, Edward McCarthy, Jr., and Charles Cook Howell, Jr., for petitioner. Will O. Murrell, for respondent. *692PER CURIAM:

The petition for certiorari to review an order of the Circuit Court, reversing an order of the Civil Court of Record granting a motion for new trial, is denied.

CHAPMAN, C. J., BROWN, BUFORD and THOMAS, JJ., concur.
